description:         Use ghczdecode <string> to decode it
homepage:            https://github.com/Peaker/ghczdecode
license:             BSD3
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Eyal Lotem
maintainer:          eyal.lotem@gmail.com
category:            Development
build-type:          Simple
